Package: arcana
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libssl3, libpcre2-8-0, libgc1, zlib1g, adduser
Description: Agent communication bus and AI provider library
 Arcana is a Crystal library and server providing a mailbox-based agent
 communication bus and provider-agnostic interfaces for chat, image, TTS,
 and embedding services. Includes an MCP bridge for Claude Code integration.
